ii'' magazine www.ioh.pl. Retrieved 12 February 2014.</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Ost Regime Change\">David Ost, ''Regime Change in Poland, Carried Out From Within''. 08 January 2016. [http://www.thenation.com/article/regime-change-in-poland-carried-out-from-within/ Regime Change in Poland]. [[The Nation]]. Retrieved 18 January 2016.</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Ost Solidarity vii\u2013ix\">David Ost, ''Solidarity and the Politics of Anti-Politics'', pp. vii\u2013ix</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Ost Solidarity 1\u20136\">David Ost, ''Solidarity and the Politics of Anti-Politics'', pp. 1\u20136</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Ost Solidarity 6\u201314\">David Ost, ''Solidarity and the Politics of Anti-Politics'', pp. 6\u201314</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Ost Solidarity 34\u201338\">David Ost, ''Solidarity and the Politics of Anti-Politics'', pp. 34\u201338, 1990 Philadelphia, [[Temple University Press]], {{ISBN|0-87722-655-5}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Ost Solidarity 38\u201349\">David Ost, ''Solidarity and the Politics of Anti-Politics'', pp. 38\u201349</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Ost Solidarity 49\u201353\">David Ost, ''Solidarity and the Politics of Anti-Politics'', pp. 49\u201353</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Ost Solidarity 55\u201358\">David Ost, ''Solidarity and the Politics of Anti-Politics'', pp. 55\u201358</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Ost Solidarity 58\u201364\">David Ost, ''Solidarity and the Politics of Anti-Politics'', pp. 58\u201364</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Ost Solidarity 67\u201370\">David Ost, ''Solidarity and the Politics of Anti-Politics'', pp. 67\u201370</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Ost Solidarity 70\u201374\">David Ost, ''Solidarity and the Politics of Anti-Politics'', pp. 70\u201374</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Ost Solidarity 75\u201379\">David Ost, ''Solidarity and the Politics of Anti-Politics'', pp. 75\u201379</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Ost Solidarity 79\u201381\">David Ost, ''Solidarity and the Politics of Anti-Politics'', pp. 79\u201381</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Ost Solidarity 81\u201385\">David Ost, ''Solidarity and the Politics of Anti-Polit